**You MUST invoke the tool like this:**

```
<invoke name="AskUserQuestion">
<parameter name="questions">[
  {
    "question": "Which errors should show the popup?",
    "header": "Error types",
    "options": [
      {"label": "All errors", "description": "Any problem shows the popup"},
      {"label": "Critical only", "description": "Only serious problems"}
    ],
    "multiSelect": false
  }
]

